        <main>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="media" id="media">
            <img id="mainImg" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542317854-4b3b3c9b7f0c?q=80&w=1600&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&s=placeholder" alt="Ruang Kuliah">
            <div class="thumbs" id="thumbs">
                <div class="thumb active" data-src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542317854-4b3b3c9b7f0c?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&s=placeholder"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542317854-4b3b3c9b7f0c?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&s=placeholder" alt="t1"></div>
                <div class="thumb" data-src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524758631624-e2822e304c36?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&s=placeholder"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524758631624-e2822e304c36?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&s=placeholder" alt="t2"></div>
                <div class="thumb" data-src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557800636-894a64c1696f?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&s=placeholder"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557800636-894a64c1696f?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&s=placeholder" alt="t3"></div>
            </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
            <div class="title">
                <div>
                <h1>Ruang Kuliah LT3-05</h1>
                <div class="sub">Gedung A • Lantai 3 • Kode: LT3-05</div>
                </div>

                <div style="text-align:right">
                <div class="muted">Kapasitas</div>
                <div style="font-weight:700">40 orang</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="meta">
                <div class="m">Jam Operasional: 07:00 — 20:00</div>
                <div class="m">Reservasi Max: 8 jam/hari</div>
                <div class="m">Verifikasi: Manual oleh Admin</div>
            </div>

            <div class="two">
                <div>
                <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0">Fasilitas</h3>
                <ul class="list">
                    <li>• Proyektor</li>
                    <li>• AC</li>
                    <li>• Whiteboard</li>
                    <li>• Koneksi LAN</li>
                </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0">Deskripsi</h3>
                <div class="list">Ruang kuliah standar untuk kapasitas 40 mahasiswa. Dekat lift, akses mudah, cocok untuk kuliah, seminar kecil, dan workshop.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-row">
                <a href="#booking" class="btn primary">Pesan Sekarang</a>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top:14px;display:flex;gap:12px">
                <div class="card" style="padding:12px;border-radius:10px;flex:1;background:#fbfbfe"> 
                <strong>Aturan Peminjaman</strong>
                <div class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">• Harap jaga kebersihan • Tidak memindah peralatan • Gunakan waktu sesuai izin</div>
                </div>

                <div class="card" style="padding:12px;border-radius:10px;flex:1;background:#fbfbfe">
                <strong>Catatan Ketersediaan</strong>
                <div class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">Lihat kalender pada bagian pemesanan untuk slot kosong. Sistem menolak tabrakan jadwal secara otomatis.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="foot-cta">
            <div>
            <div style="font-weight:700">Butuh konfirmasi cepat?</div>
            <div class="muted">Hubungi admin ruang jika perlu verifikasi mendesak.</div>
            </div>
            <div><a href="#contact" class="btn" style="color:var(--muted);background:var(--card);border:1px solid #e7eafc;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px">Hubungi Admin</a></div>
        </div>
        </main>

        <aside class="aside">
        <div class="panel" id="booking">
            <div style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px">Formulir Peminjaman</div>
            <form id="bookingForm">
            <div class="row">
                <label for="date">Tanggal</label>
                <input id="date" name="date" type="date" required />
            </div>

            <div style="display:flex;gap:8px">
                <div style="flex:1" class="row">
                <label for="start">Mulai</label>
                <input id="start" name="start" type="time" required />
                </div>
                <div style="flex:1" class="row">
                <label for="end">Selesai</label>
                <input id="end" name="end" type="time" required />
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <label for="name">Penanggung Jawab (Nama / NIM / Ormawa)</label>
                <input id="name" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Nama / NIM / Organisasi" required />
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <label for="note">Catatan (opsional)</label>
                <textarea id="note" name="note" rows="3" placeholder="Butuh alat tambahan / catatan"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div id="msg"></div>
            <button type="submit">Kirim Permintaan</button>
            <div class="small-info">Setelah dikirim, admin akan memverifikasi. Anda akan menerima notifikasi di dashboard atau email.</div>
            </form>

            <div class="similar">
            <h4 style="margin:12px 0 8px 0">Ruangan Serupa</h4>
            <a href="#">LT3-06 — Ruang Kuliah <span class="muted">• Kapasitas 40</span></a>
            <a href="#">LT2-01 — Ruang Seminar <span class="muted">• Kapasitas 60</span></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        </aside>
    </div>
</div>

